Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.92,0:19:18.92,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord3\3c&H5F6FA4&}どんぐりころころ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:20.72,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord3\3c&H5F6FA4&}ドンブリコ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.13,0:19:23.09,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord3\3c&H5F6FA4&}お池にはまって
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:24.85,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord3\3c&H5F6FA4&}さあ大変
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:27.35,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord3\3c&H5F6FA4&}どじょうが出て来て
