Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.92,0:19:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,橡子咕噜咕噜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滚啊滚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.13,0:19:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掉进池塘里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泥鳅跑出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.39,0:19:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.39,0:19:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我们一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.73,0:19:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能看到小雏的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.15,0:19:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说实话我真是松了一口气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.82,0:19:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论是大学还是这个镇子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.41,0:19:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遇到的都是好人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是走运
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.58,0:19:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家人真的是不可思议啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.17,0:19:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算两个人也是一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.46,0:19:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算分开也还是一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.71,0:19:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算没有血缘关系也是一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们四个人会一直守护的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.97,0:20:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种成为家人的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.89,0:20:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永远  永远
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多了  准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕  有点想尿尿了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.27,0:20:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行  不准尿尿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.36,0:20:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大伙不在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥\N舅舅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.12,0:20:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感谢你为我们所做的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.09,0:20:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舅舅是爸爸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.09,0:20:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给  小雏给你的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.34,0:20:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.39,0:20:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你让我们得到了幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.39,0:20:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小雏  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.85,0:20:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想吃蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.14,0:20:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有蛋糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.98,0:20:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.81,0:20:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那来拍张照片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.61,0:21:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起  来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.65,0:21:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要拍的话  先让我换件衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.07,0:21:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶？就拍张照而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.49,0:21:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准偷看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.03,0:21:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经憋不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.45,0:21:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.29,0:21:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕  蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.79,0:21:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是都说了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.34,0:21:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来  撞到哪里啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.05,0:21:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个  很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.84,0:21:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你先出去下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.93,0:21:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个  拍照呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.43,0:21:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有比这个更重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.97,0:21:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕  蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.73,0:21:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舅舅  开开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.77,0:21:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说反了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.90,0:21:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.23,0:21:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开的时候先说一声啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.87,0:21:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.08,0:21:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕  蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.12,0:21:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  够了  你们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:21:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要听爸爸的话！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.55,0:23:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.63,0:23:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
